[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The problem statement is exceptional. The "medical knowledge doubles every 73 days" hook immediately establishes urgency, and the precision medicine scenario (rare genetic variant, answer buried in a paper from three weeks ago) makes the abstract problem concrete and human.
