[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The technology section's treatment of the NLP pipeline is comprehensive and honest. The discussion of negation detection ("Missing negation detection is one of the fastest ways to poison your knowledge graph with false positives") is exactly the kind of practical wisdom that distinguishes this cookbook from generic architecture documentation.
